title: Pennsylvania Department of Health, Hospices, Pennsylvania, 2007
name: Pennsylvania Department of Health, Hospices, Pennsylvania, 2007
description:
Abstract:

Pennsylvania hospices from the Department of Health's quality assurance database.  Current as of 10/29/2007.

Purpose:

This layer was developed for use in emergency situations and for the general public.

Supplemental_Information:

The hospice addresses were geocoded.  Geocoding of addresses creates points of estimated locations.  These locations were not verified.  The user should assume that there is some spacial error.
